{"tid":2095820,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載] 請問各位男士怎麼小便","createTime":"2020-07-05T18:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T02:15:15.000Z","uid":3522,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"823cf54b3b9b2a6778a6371bc70f13a766034450","tid":2095820,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:21:38.000Z","msg":"原文: <a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/marriage/M.1593953966.A.6DE.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fmarriage%2FM.1593953966.A.6DE.htm&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=65306534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/marriage/M.1593953966.A.6DE.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n今天早上發生一件讓我非常崩潰的事情。<br />\n<br />\n 那就是 ....<br />\n<br />\n我發現我老公在浴室的洗手台尿尿 &hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我是在洗手檯邊緣發現尿漬才讓我知道這件事&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n而他竟然一臉不以為意說有沖乾淨啊！<br />\n<br />\n天啊 ！而且這不是一次的行為&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n是每次小解都是在洗手台尿，<br />\n<br />\n我真的要崩潰了！<br />\n<br />\n我女兒身高剛好比洗手台高一點點<br />\n<br />\n 早上漱口都會碰觸到洗手檯。<br />\n<br />\n且我們的蓮蓬頭沒有掛著，<br />\n<br />\n都是放在洗手台，<br />\n<br />\n也就是我每天都用可能沾有尿液的蓮蓬頭洗澡，<br />\n<br />\n怎麼有人衛生習慣如此噁心，<br />\n<br />\n他就辯說他無法在馬桶尿，<br />\n<br />\n會噴得到處都是，也無法坐，<br />\n<br />\n也會噴，他184公分，<br />\n<br />\n他是說太高所以會噴，<br />\n<br />\n噴在地上如果用水沖會讓地板潮濕，<br />\n<br />\n所以才在洗手台尿&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n請問各位男士到底怎麼樣小便是最好的方式呢！<br />\n感謝各位"},{"pid":"8f1a291b20d7b1e267fca7d0063eee5499bf7025","tid":2095820,"uid":3522,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:23:23.000Z","msg":"睇完之後好驚有痴線佬喺公廁啲洗手盤度痾尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188cb8d5d51f366dcb4a7fd8cc56e7a8f098625f","tid":2095820,"uid":16567,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:23:30.000Z","msg":"痾出窗外面"},{"pid":"f7a62092e6e26e7b8f8731ff9d4e4a48b4b262a1","tid":2095820,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f1a291b20d7b1e267fca7d0063eee5499bf7025","tid":2095820,"uid":3522,"like":2,"dislik